  "description": "Pardon the intrusion, sir, but ten corpus anchors for the kor — the Zendikar-native plate-armored nomadic warrior race — was firmly above the team-rocket / acerola / orzhov-syndicate threshold. Eight BFZ-block kor cards (3 explicitly Kor-named: Bladewhirl, Castigator, Entanglers; 5 implicit: Kitesail Scout, Expedition Envoy, Cliffside Lookout, Shadow Glider, Unified Front) plus one ZNR successor (Farsight Adept) and one OGW continuation (Kor Sky Climber, prep-stub). The node cross-edges to eldrazi.md as canonical BFZ adversaries — the two faction nodes form a mutual adversary-coupling that anchors any BFZ-block Discrete Lair. I hope this proves helpful for the BFZ-bundle pipeline, sir.",
